---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Layout from '../../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
import AboutLogo from '../../assets/logo2.png';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="My journey"
	pubDate={new Date('June 03 2026')}
>
	<div class="about-logo">
		<Image src={AboutLogo} width={160} height={160} alt="B4NGG logo" />
	</div>

	<p>
		Hi! My name is Alex, although online I usually go by the nickname <strong>B4NGG</strong>.
	</p>

	<p>
		I am a software engineer and I am currently focusing my path toward cybersecurity. I have
		always been interested in this field, but for a long time I did not decide to fully make the
		jump. Although software development and cybersecurity complement each other, they also have
		very different approaches and challenges.
	</p>

	<p>
		I created this blog to document my cybersecurity journey and share what I learn along the way:
		machines, certifications, methodologies, mistakes, notes, and personal experiences.
	</p>

	<p>
		I also started a Spanish-language YouTube channel as a complement to this blog. There, I share some experiences, advice, and lessons learned in a more dynamic way.

	</p>

	<p>
		My goal is to learn in public and leave the path documented, hoping that it can also help
		someone else.
	</p>

	<style>
		.about-logo {
			display: flex;
			justify-content: center;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}

		.about-logo img {
			width: 150px;
			height: 150px;
			object-fit: contain;
			border-radius: 999px;
			background: #000;
			padding: 1rem;
			border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
			box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		}
	</style>
</Layout>